metadata.name: LabGoblinZ #1
metadata.description: Warning! Warning! Warning! 10000 LabGoblinZ are the shadowy intentions of the old deceased Labcoats manifested as a physical being and are running amuck in the lab. So, in our attempt to keep them from creating chaos from within the dark. We need the strength of the Kongz to unite and keep these shadowy beings in check. We have a feeling though that some of you might get attached and want to start Collecting these LabGoblinZ and some of you will also turn on a profit from trading these wicked beings. Either way, Alphas & Omegas we call upon you to help us take on the First Waves!!!
